<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.7">
<l>ilaiyār malarppūm poykaivāy mutalai taṉṉā laṭarppuṇṭu</l>
<l>kolaiyār vēḻam naṭukkuṟṟuk kulaiya vataṉuk karuḷpurintāṉ</l>
<l>alainī rilaṅkait tacakkirīvaṟ kiḷaiyōṟ karacai yaruḷimuṉ</l>
<l>kalaimāc cilaiyā leytāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram, the city of him</l>
<l rend="indent">who once shot the male deer with a bow,</l>
<l>Granting the kingdom of Laṅkā with crashing seas</l>
<l rend="indent">to the younger brother of the ten-necked one,</l>
<l>Of him who bestowed grace to a torment-filled elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">feeling tremors, so [it] was freed,</l>
<l>[After] having been afflicted by a crocodile</l>
<l rend="indent">in a flourishing pond with petal-filled blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
